precis:
Enactment of the REPRODUCTION OF FEDERAL LAW ORDER which provides that
anyone may, without charge or request for permission, reproduce enactments
of the Government of Canada or consolidations thereof, and decisions of
federally-constituted courts and tribunals and the reasons for same.
